# ── LLM provider (powers the Ask chat + the parent report card) ──────────────
# Set ONE provider key. Auto-detected priority: gemini > groq > perplexity > openai.
# Without any key, the app still works via curated fallbacks.

# ⭐ RECOMMENDED — FREE, NO CREDIT CARD:
# Google Gemini (free tier ~1,500 req/day). Get a key at https://aistudio.google.com → "Get API key".
GEMINI_API_KEY=
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash

# Also free, no card: Groq (fast). Get a key at https://console.groq.com/keys
# GROQ_API_KEY=
# GROQ_MODEL=llama-3.3-70b-versatile

# Paid options (OpenAI-compatible):
# PERPLEXITY_API_KEY=        # perplexity.ai → Settings → API
# PERPLEXITY_MODEL=sonar
# OPENAI_API_KEY=            # platform.openai.com (NOT the ChatGPT subscription)
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini

# Optional: force a provider (gemini | groq | perplexity | openai)
# LLM_PROVIDER=gemini

# Optional: Google Sheet login logging via an Apps Script Web App webhook.
# Set this to your deployed Apps Script /exec URL to append every login
# (timestamp + email) to your sheet. See README "Login logging → Google Sheet".
# Without it, logins still append to a local .login-log.jsonl file.
SHEETS_WEBHOOK_URL=
